  "body": "## Description\r\nCurrently `lighthouse account validator import` subcommand only supports reading password interactively or reading from stdin.\r\n\r\n## The problem\r\nIn environments like Kubernetes, container can't read input from stdin and can't work interactively\r\n\r\n### Version\r\nwe're using latest released version `v1.1.3`\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n`lighthouse account validator import` should accept `--password-path` that reads password from file.\r\n",
